reviewText:
After approx. 5 weeks, I am still waiting for the item to arrive!
Not acceptable!

My son wants the software, but the package we got doesn't work.  Some of the disks are missing data and others make funny sounds and crank very slowly in the DVD drive, which does work because other CDs work in the drive.  It's a new Macbook - only a couple of months old.  I need to send back the software and get another set.
